      "acceptanceCriteria": "FEA software (Ansys) under institutional SQA plan; version-controlled input files; regression test suite passing.",
      "rationale": "Ansys Mechanical 2022R2 operated under a documented SQA plan meeting FDA software guidance. Version control (Git) applied to all model input files. Regression test suite executed with no failures. Achieved level meets required level for Medium model risk."
    },
    {
